{"v":7,"a":[7],"p":[{"b":18,"e":"SINCE I JOINED HERE :
I have felt very welcome in this community
compared to previous groups in various
other games and websites.
I understand that the minute number
of active members on this game makes it
a lot easier for everyone to become fast friends.
I would like to stay a part of this community
and continue to support it for as long as
I do so","s":[{"p":[0,0,0],"r":[0,0,0],"s":[0.003000033,0.003000013,0.003000042],"c":[1,1,1]}]}]}

{"v":7,"a":[7],"p":[{"b":18,"e":"BEING A NEWCOMER:
It was very strange being on a social VR game.
Granted this wasn't my first time since i had been
on VRCHAT already but I lacked the confidence 
to say anything so to say I didn't feel like I fitted
in is a simple way to put it.
Anyland had a lot of people who actually wanted
to help and talk to me which made me feel a
lot more confident and actually want to stay.","s":[{"p":[0,0,0],"r":[0,0,0],"s":[0.003000083,0.002999993,0.003000076],"c":[1,1,1]}]}]}

{"v":7,"a":[7],"p":[{"b":18,"e":"CREATING MY FIRST WORLD:
Their were a lot of things I wanted to get started
on, one of the main things being a world to call my own.
I had seen a few world by now with the help of Axel,
one of the older members of the community, but
one that inspired me the most was Evencrom Forest,
a map made by Ben that looked like a dark forest
area with a 'hidden' passage leading to an unfinished tomb.
My idea was to have my own take on that, although
I didn't want to overwelm myself so early on and my
 idea changed to a 'simpler' one.","s":[{"p":[0,0,0],"r":[0,0,0],"s":[0.003000082,0.003000013,0.003000057],"c":[1,1,1]}]}]}

{"v":7,"a":[7],"p":[{"b":18,"e":"CREATING MY FIRST AVITAR:
I've noticed that a lot of people go for robots when
it comes to body designs, and I really wasn't any
diffrent in my case
I had started with a floating clock tower island but
that was just a placeholder until I had a better
idea of what I wanted to be remembered by.
I eventually came up with a sort of simple 
double pyramid shaped floating droid (for lack
of a better description) and just went with that
to avoid over thinking.","s":[{"p":[0,0,0],"r":[0,0,0],"s":[0.003000082,0.003000013,0.003000057],"c":[1,1,1]}]}]}

{"v":7,"a":[7],"p":[{"b":18,"e":"MAKING FRIENDS:
It wasn't exactly as easy as it could have been.
My past experiances have led me to become
very wary of getting too comfortable around
others.
A lot of the people here acted a little bit too
crazy for my comfort but , as I got to meet 
and understand more people, I genuinly enjoyed
my time with them.
I'm still very picky with my friends but people
like Ben and Zid are the sort of people who
,I feel, are good friends.","s":[{"p":[0,0,0],"r":[0,0,0],"s":[0.003000082,0.003000013,0.003000057],"c":[1,1,1]}]}]}

{"v":7,"a":[7],"p":[{"b":18,"e":"THE COMMUNITY:
Despite it's size, the people who play this do
help out a lot when it comes to trying to keep
this game afloat and even thrive. I may be 
exadurating a little but I have seen loyal
members spend a lot of time and effort into
worlds which aim to bring more people to
this game.
Unfortunatly, most of the newcomers i've met
don't tend to stay longer than a day let alone
a week.
In the end, I hope the game pulls through for
the dev team.","s":[{"p":[0,0,0],"r":[0,0,0],"s":[0.003000082,0.003000013,0.003000057],"c":[1,1,1]}]}]}

{"v":7,"a":[7],"p":[{"b":18,"e":"CONGRATULATIONS:
All you have found here is an attempt to preserve
a fading memory, even as I am typing this, the
feelings and experiances described here become
more distant and distorted.
Maybe you found this area by accident,
prehaps you're more invested in finding secrets,
it may be that someone told you about this
maybe it was me.
Whatever the reason is I hope this gave you some
insight into how my first days were or at least
pleasure in finding this maps most hidden area.
I hope that you have a pleasant day and that 
Im still holding it together if you find me to.
Thank you for reading.","s":[{"p":[0,0,0],"r":[0,0,0],"s":[0.003000082,0.003000013,0.003000057],"c":[1,1,1]}]}]}
